OL,3,CWait times at hospital's emergency
OL,4,Cdepartment still 'too long', CQC
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FDerriford Hospital's emergency
OL,8,Fdepartment is still experiencing
OL,9,Fovercrowding and long delays, the
OL,10,Fhealthcare watchdog has warned.
OL,12,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,13,Finspected the department unannounced
OL,14,Fin March and issued a warning notice
OL,15,Ffor bosses to make "rapid and
OL,16,Fwidespread improvements" to fix
OL,17,Fovercrowding and ambulance handover
OL,18,Ftimes, before July.
