OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FFollowing a recent re-inspection, the
OL,8,FCQC said while the hospital's
OL,9,Femergency services are now better they
OL,10,Fstill "require improvement."
OL,12,FThe overall rating for the University
OL,13,FHospitals Plymouth NHS Trust and
OL,14,FDerriford Hospital remains "requires
OL,15,Fimprovement." The CQC says it will
OL,16,Fcontinue to monitor standards.
