OL,3,CWait times at hospital's emergency
OL,4,Cdepartment still 'too long', CQC
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FAfter releasing the most recent
OL,8,Freport, following re-inspection,
OL,9,FCatherine Campbell, CQC's deputy
OL,10,Fdirector of operations in the south,
OL,11,Fsaid: "On previous inspections we had
OL,12,Fhighlighted the pressures at Derriford
OL,13,FHospital being mainly due to limited
OL,14,Favailability of social care beds and
OL,15,Fcommunity care, which impacted on the
OL,16,Fnumber of medically fit people able to
OL,17,Fbe discharged.
OL,19,F"That hindered flow throughout the
OL,20,Fhospital, causing people to experience
OL,21,Flong delays.
OL,26,@sD@GOU
