OL,3,CWait times at hospital's emergency
OL,4,Cdepartment still 'too long', CQC
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,F"During this inspection we found
OL,8,Fpeople were still experiencing long
OL,9,Fwaits in ambulances and the emergency
OL,10,Fdepartment waiting room was still
OL,11,Fovercrowded.
OL,13,F"This included people experiencing
OL,14,Flong waits to be triaged, treated or
OL,15,Fdischarged. One person's relative was
OL,16,Ftold there may be a 48 hour wait for
OL,17,Ftheir loved one to be admitted to
OL,18,Fhospital.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
