OL,3,CWait times at hospital's emergency
OL,4,Cdepartment still 'too long', CQC
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,F"However, some told us they had been
OL,8,Fassessed and treated relatively
OL,9,Fquickly. People gave positive feedback
OL,10,Fabout staff, describing them as
OL,11,Fbrilliant and lovely.
OL,13,F"This doesn't alter the fact that in
OL,14,FOctober 2021, we highlighted the same
OL,15,Fproblems to the trust's leadership and
OL,16,Flocal stakeholders."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
