OL,3,CWait times at hospital's emergency
OL,4,Cdepartment still 'too long', CQC
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FIt added: "The new leadership team
OL,8,Fwere building relationships internally
OL,9,Fand externally with local
OL,10,Fstakeholders, ambulance services and
OL,11,FGPs. Weekly meetings with the
OL,12,Fambulance service had helped to
OL,13,Fjointly manage the high numbers of
OL,14,Fpeople arriving by ambulance.
OL,16,F"We will continue to monitor the
OL,17,Ftrust, including through future
OL,18,Finspections, to ensure the necessary
OL,19,Fimprovements are made so people can
OL,20,Freceive safe and appropriate care."
