OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FResponse from University Hospitals
OL,8,FPlymouth NHS Trust
OL,10,FA statement from the trust responds:
OL,11,F"Staff at University Hospitals
OL,12,FPlymouth NHS Trust have made
OL,13,Fconsiderable improvements for patients
OL,14,Farriving as emergencies following a
OL,15,FCQC inspection, but they know there is
OL,16,Fmore to do.
OL,18,F"Inspectors visited back in March of
OL,19,Fthis year and have just published
OL,20,Ftheir report which has been delayed
OL,21,Fdue to IT issues at the CQC.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
