OL,3,CWait times at hospital's emergency
OL,4,Cdepartment still 'too long', CQC
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,F"They carried out an inspection of
OL,8,FUrgent and Emergency Care (UEC), Same
OL,9,FDay Emergency Care and the Discharge
OL,10,FLounge, over two days.
OL,12,F"At the time, the CQC arrived during
OL,13,Fan internal Critical Incident and saw
OL,14,Fthe reality of a crowded busy
OL,15,FEmergency Department with significant
OL,16,Fnumbers of ambulances waiting,
OL,17,Fspeaking to both staff, patients and
OL,18,Fpartner organisations."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
