OL,3,CWait times at hospital's emergency
OL,4,Cdepartment still 'too long', CQC
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FInterim Chief Executive Mark Hackett
OL,8,Fadded: "At the time, we know the
OL,9,Fquality and speed of care we were able
OL,10,Fto offer patients coming for Urgent
OL,11,Fand Emergency Care was not what we
OL,12,Faspire it to be when the CQC inspected
OL,13,Four services back in early March.
OL,15,F"They arrived during an internal
OL,16,FCritical Incident and what they saw
OL,17,Fwas fairly reflected in their report,
OL,18,Fbut that was eight months ago now and
OL,19,Fwe have made good progress in
OL,20,Fimproving our performance since then.
