OL,3,CWait times at hospital's emergency
OL,4,Cdepartment still 'too long', CQC
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FJo Beer, the chief operating officer
OL,8,Fof University Hospitals Plymouth NHS
OL,9,FTrust, added: "What we're seeing with
OL,10,Fthe new model of care is that actually
OL,11,Fwhen we do have those periods where we
OL,12,Fhave high levels of demand, really
OL,13,Fsick patients, we are recovering much
OL,14,Fquicker.
OL,16,F"So instead of one to two weeks to get
OL,17,Fourselves back into shape, it's one to
OL,18,Fthree days, one to two days sometimes."
