OL,7,FCommenting on the report, Fred Thomas,
OL,8,FMP for Plymouth Moor View, said: "This
OL,9,Freport highlights why I am campaigning
OL,10,Fso hard for a new A&E department at
OL,11,FDerriford. We need it."
OL,13,FHe added: "Today's CQC report shows
OL,14,Fthe cost of these broken promises. I
OL,15,Fwill continue working with staff at
OL,16,FDerriford to campaign for a new A&E."
